=e32e7804&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/21/140239_156e131c9148f45674237d7a3cfd5e7e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F21%2F140239_156e131c9148f45674237d7a3cfd5e7e.jpg&h=a6c76468&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/21/140241_9e078cd8259f4fb25f9be72d543b8951.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F21%2F140241_9e078cd8259f4fb25f9be72d543b8951.jpg&h=3c111c5d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/21/140247_aef0ba8c76c2b0cd0c6433a3f4f0273d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F21%2F140247_aef0ba8c76c2b0cd0c6433a3f4f0273d.jpg&h=a9a23fc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n樓主一定要去伯利恆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個圍牆超靚"},{"pid":"366a6c87b8d2477fc2746b49eb47ef9ee8560a41","tid":292104,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T06:05:41.000Z","msg":"又呃正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1585fbb1b3475fc3d1a30e096a00355afaa2922","tid":292104,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T06:06:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/21/135353_9c9f8c4c53946c4c4ee4b10df82eaccf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F21%2F135353_9c9f8c4c53946c4c4ee4b10df82eaccf.jpg&h=d5c49231&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n早2個星期去完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲好講，無包膠<br />\n<br />\n等我上登機橋行咗右邊，中咗抽樣檢查<br />\n<br />\n上到機，頭頂個行李倉都無位。<br />\n<br />\n枉我仲排得好前</blockquote><br />\n一定係你個樣好毒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過真係預早4個鐘去機場好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我係hostel book車個時條友仲叫我早3個鐘去就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好彩我早左4個鐘去<br />\n俾人check左2次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一次係行李一次係個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後得返15分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我講梗香港喎，登機橋要CHECK，等我仲一早去機場，結果喺閘口附近上網用APP睇電視。<br />\n<br />\n以色列出境，我乜事都無。<br />\n<br />\n出境我早咗差唔多四個鐘去到，未做得CHECK IN，又唔知原來要做一次 SECURITY CHECK 先可以做1CHECK IN，等我排咗幾個字去到CHECK IN先知又要出番去做SECURITY CHECK，只係齋問問題，做都咗都無1個字，所有行李無開過。<br />\n<br />\n真正既安檢都無截停，啲嘢就咁過就得喎。<br />\n<br />\n你應該毒過我好多。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61243d5a0b1beb5fba605aa0e0bbb9b1f02ecf1a","tid":292104,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T06:07:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/21/140235_dcbb2db6e0b31a742c4d1de743c5c232.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F21%2F140235_dcbb2db6e0b31a742c4d1de743c5c232.jpg&h=160bcea2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/21/140237_997d9e0eecffb738263cc7d4d14f96f1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F21%2F140237_997d9e0eecffb738263cc7d4d14f96f1.jpg&h=e32e7804&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/21/140239_156e131c9148f45674237d7a3cfd5e7e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F21%2F140239_156e131c9148f45674237d7a3cfd5e7e.jpg&h=a6c76468&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/21/140241_9e078cd8259f4fb25f9be72d543b8951.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F21%2F140241_9e078cd8259f4fb25f9be72d543b8951.jpg&h=3c111c5d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/21/140247_aef0ba8c76c2b0cd0c6433a3f4f0273d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F21%2F140247_aef0ba8c76c2b0cd0c6433a3f4f0273d.jpg&h=a9a23fc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n樓主一定要去伯利恆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個圍牆超靚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n返咗嚟啦。<br />\n<br />\n伯利恆諗起就扯火，去希律堡遇着不知所謂白牌司機。"},{"pid":"2b34c9246c6d29f7f5883c7cc4b417dbf0a19edf","tid":292104,"uid":8105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T06:10:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/21/135353_9c9f8c4c53946c4c4ee4b10df82eaccf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F21%2F135353_9c9f8c4c53946c4c4ee4b10df82eaccf.jpg&h=d5c49231&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n早2個星期去完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲好講，無包膠<br />\n<br />\n等我上登機橋行咗右邊，中咗抽樣檢查<br />\n<br />\n上到機，頭頂個行李倉都無位。<br />\n<br />\n枉我仲排得好前</blockquote><br />\n一定係你個樣好毒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過真係預早4個鐘去機場好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我係hostel book車個時條友仲叫我早3個鐘去就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好彩我早左4個鐘去<br />\n俾人check左2次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一次係行李一次係個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後得返15分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />